Initial Setup

1. Ensure Flipper Zero has fresh batteries
2. Install application via SD card
3. Launch from application menu

Scanning Procedure

1. Positioning: Hold device at chest height in area to be scanned
2. Initiate Scan: Press Right button to start scanning
3. Movement: Slowly sweep device across room, focusing on suspicious areas
4. Monitoring: Watch for threat indicators and listen for vibration alerts
5. Investigation: When threat detected, investigate indicated frequency area

Threat Response Protocol

路 Level 1-2 Threats: Conduct visual inspection of area
路 Level 3 Threats: Detailed physical examination recommended
路 Level 4 Threats: Immediate security assessment required

Real-World Applications

 Travel Security

路 Hotel room inspections
路 Airbnb and vacation rental safety checks
路 Conference room privacy verification

 Home & Office

路 Private residence security audits
路 Office space surveillance detection
路 Locker room and bathroom privacy checks

