Technical Architecture

Core Components

路 SubGhz Integration: Leverages Flipper's radio capabilities for signal analysis
路 View Management: Efficient UI rendering with model-view separation
路 Notification System: Multi-channel alert delivery (vibration, LED, sound)
路 Timer Management: Precise scanning intervals and resource cleanup

Signal Processing

```c
// Threat assessment algorithm
1. Frequency matching against known camera databases
2. RSSI strength evaluation (-75 dBm threshold)
3. Signal pattern analysis
4. Threat level calculation (1-4 scale)
5. Multi-factor confirmation to reduce false positives
```

Performance Characteristics

路 Memory Usage: ~4KB stack size, efficient heap management
路 Battery Impact: Optimized scanning intervals for extended operation
路 Scan Efficiency: 100ms intervals provide real-time responsiveness
路 Accuracy: High detection rate with minimal false positives
